SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "users" WHERE "users"."created_at" BETWEEN $? AND $?

SELECT axis.*, ( WITH new_users AS ( SELECT users.id FROM users WHERE date_trunc(?, users.created_at)::date = axis.period ) SELECT count(*) FROM new_users ) AS value FROM ( SELECT generate_series(date_trunc(?, ?::timestamp)::date, date_trunc(?, ?::timestamp)::date, interval ?) AS period ) AS axis
